{
  "market_read": "Market is holding up reasonably well with Nifty near 24,046 despite US-Iran escalation headwinds — breadth is positive (1.64 A/D ratio) and VIX has eased to 18. Strong Q4 earnings from M&M (+42% PAT), TATATECH, BHEL, and WOCKPHARMA are driving stock-specific moves, while auto sector benefits from record April sales data. Key risks remain elevated crude (~$110), rupee at record lows (95.39), and geopolitical tail risk — these argue for disciplined position sizing and avoiding new heavy commitments in oil-sensitive names.",
  "watchlist": [
    {
      "symbol": "PNBHOUSING",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Currently held (+6.1% unrealized). Need full data to assess whether to trail SL, hold, or take partial profits near end of session."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "GOLDBEES",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Currently held (-2.4% unrealized). Gold ETF in portfolio as macro hedge — with Middle East escalation and rupee at record lows, need to reassess hold vs exit thesis."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "ADANIPORTS",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Currently held (+2.1% unrealized). Up nicely; SCI +5.69% showing port/logistics sector strength. Need to check if SL should be trailed up to lock in gains."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "MARUTI",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Currently held (-2.4% unrealized). April sales record (+35% YoY) is a strong catalyst but stock down 25% from Jan peak and currently negative. Need to reassess thesis vs SL proximity."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "BANDHANBNK",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Currently held (-0.6% unrealized). Banking sector mixed today; need to check technical levels and whether thesis still intact for holding overnight."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "M&M",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Q4 PAT +42-53% YoY (standalone), dividend Rs 33/share declared, April SUVs +8% YoY. Strong beat — up +1.84% today, potential swing entry after earnings confirmation."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "BHEL",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Up +6.28% post strong Q4 results, near 52-week high range. Capex/infra theme strong. Need full data to assess if momentum entry is justified or if it's overextended intraday."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "TATATECH",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Up +7.28% post Q4 beat (PAT +8%, revenue +22%). On previous watchlist. Need to check if the move has legs or if Motilal's 15% downside call creates a sell-the-news ceiling."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "ADANIGREEN",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Up +8.38% today, within 4.6% of 52-week high, strong volume on energy/renewables theme. Need full data to assess breakout quality vs cluster risk (already hold ADANIPORTS)."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "HAL",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Up +6.48% with defence sector momentum. Previously on watchlist. With geopolitical escalation driving defence spending narratives, need full data on technical setup and valuation."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "LALPATHLAB",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Gapped up +14.8% at open, currently +12.21% — likely Q4 earnings beat. Pharma sector outperforming. Need full data to see if there's still momentum or if the gap has been faded."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "WOCKPHARMA",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Up +9.53% on strong Q4 turnaround (profit turned positive, revenue surge). Pharma sector strength. Need full data to evaluate conviction for a swing entry."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "VEDL",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Up +11.23% on 3.2x volume, demerger catalyst with four new entities expected by mid-June. Metals sector leading. Need full data to assess if the demerger story supports continued upside."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "CAMS",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Up +7.92% on 1.9x volume — likely Q4 earnings beat in financial services. Mutual fund flows into midcaps theme. Previously on watchlist, need full data."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "NAVINFLUOR",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Up +2.59% on 7.7x volume surge — massive institutional activity signal in specialty chemicals. Previously on watchlist. Need full data to determine if this is accumulation ahead of results."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "NIFTYBEES",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Broad market ETF on previous watchlist. With cash at 51%, assessing whether deploying into index ETF is better than single-name risk given geopolitical uncertainty and thin Asia liquidity today."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "MEESHO",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "Up +8.68% on 8.8x volume surge, gapped up +13.1%. Consumer services/e-commerce with strong institutional volume. Need full data to check if this is a genuine catalyst-driven move or a pump."
    },
    {
      "symbol": "COLPAL",
      "exchange": "NSE",
      "reason": "FMCG defensive play +3.46% today — Dabur +3.82%, HINDUNILVR +3.00% showing FMCG rotation. With INR weakness and crude spike, defensive FMCG could outperform. Previously on watchlist."
    }
  ],
  "drop_from_watchlist": ["FLUOROCHEM", "SOBHA"],
  "drop_reasons": "FLUOROCHEM up +3.49% on 5.2x volume but specialty chemicals thesis needs a cleaner catalyst; NAVINFLUOR on 7.7x volume is the better chemicals expression for today. SOBHA already had its 9.5-10% move on Q4 results beat (+124% profit) — the gap has played out, too late to enter at this stage intraday, and the Realty sector is the worst performer today (-1.29%) suggesting the move is stock-specific and fading."
}
